The paper deals with a communication system involving channel gains, power constraints, and transmission schemes, which are all related to information theory (cs.IT). The use of a relay and the consideration of power allocation strategies suggest a focus on networking and communication (cs.NI). The paper also involves optimization and convex programming, which are topics in systems and control (cs.SY). The use of lattice decoding and numerical results suggest a focus on multimedia and image processing (cs.MM) and computer networks (cs.COM).
